<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="ida88f24af-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2004—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/108/375">Pub. L. 108–375</ref> substituted “more than 30 days” for “less than one year” in pars. (1) and (2).</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2000—Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/106/398">Pub. L. 106–398</ref> substituted “subparagraph” for “subparagraphs”.</p>
